    "From 1960 until 1981, Roland Michel regularly contributed articles to <em>Burlington</em>\u2019s supplement on the eighteenth century, writing on artists like Jean-Honor\u00e9 Fragonard (1732-1806), Hubert Robert (1733-1808), and Nicolas Lancret (1690-1743), among others.": [
