    "She completed a doctoral degree at the Sorbonne in 1983 under the supervision of <a href=\"/thuillierj\">Jacques Thuillier</a> with a dissertation on the painter of Rococo interiors, Jacques de Lajo\u00fce (1686-1761), which was published the following year as Lajo\u00fce et l\u2019art rocaille (1984).": [],
